{"tid":676661,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"耶耶：我想同普巴做隊友","createTime":"2018-05-24T14:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T01:26:04.000Z","uid":35598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58ee245e717bd2da0852bce102592fe769e496e1","tid":676661,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/news/view?id=309086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transfermarkt.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fview%3Fid%3D309086&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=84a5f4a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/news/view?id=309086</a><br />\n喺曼城效力八季嘅中場耶耶托尼今夏約滿，依家佢搵緊新東家，而佢表示仲想留喺高水平賽事度踢。<br />\n日前耶耶托尼接受訪問時講到想同普巴做隊友。<br />\n耶耶托尼：「我愛普巴。大眾媒體嘅意見令到佢踢得好艱難，不過認真講句，我好想同佢做隊友，分享下我啲經驗俾佢。」<br />\n記者問道會唔會考慮正接過檔曼聯，耶耶托尼：「都係不了，班顛嘅城迷會殺咗我。」<br />\n話雖如此，訪問中耶耶托尼透露想加盟一支爭標球隊，而從佢嘅口風，英超球隊似乎係首選。<br />\n耶耶托尼：「如果有日我要倒戈曼城，咁會係好困難，不過都要照踢，因為呢份係我嘅工作。」"},{"pid":"db22a6f9817440ac51b4c5818826b1a227d49558","tid":676661,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"留名睇agger路入黎發癲"},{"pid":"0ca9a3059d6d057ff7b435a2ce6c305110bb6740","tid":676661,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db22a6f9817440ac51b4c5818826b1a227d49558","tid":676661,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"留名睇agger路入黎發癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T20:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13af2204018cc41a9ca39230cb3a2ea0e0f2c4bc","tid":676661,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T21:02:30.000Z","msg":"條友係咪gay架"},{"pid":"a4fbbd552008b061f590b52e597c7ae53662b1cf","tid":676661,"uid":10392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:53:30.000Z","msg":"廣東話講得幾好"},{"pid":"4aae22010fadbe7a50f7c12868d5f99dbfd80d78","tid":676661,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0